mixin header-footer()
	.header-footer
		.header-footer-work-hours
			.header-footer-work-hours__icon
			.header-footer-work-hours__text Круглосуточно
		.header-footer-social
			.header-footer-social__text Мы в социальных сетях:
			.header-footer-social__icons
				A(href="http://instagram.com").header-footer-social__icon.header-footer-social__icon--instagram
				A(href="http://vk.com").header-footer-social__icon.header-footer-social__icon--vk
		.header-footer-telephone
			.header-footer-telephone__icon
			.header-footer-telephone__number +7-926-159-82-62
